sentence: what is the abbreviation for canadian airlines international
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.airline_code||'"', '"'||v0.airline_name||'"' FROM airline v0 
WHERE (v0.airline_name LIKE '%CANADIAN AIRLINES INTERNATIONAL%');
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE FROM AIRLINE WHERE AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME LIKE '% CANADIAN AIRLINES INTERNATIONAL %' ) ;
